<body class="slides zoom horizontal noPreload animated ">


      <section class="slide kenBurns">
        <div class="content">
          <div class="container">
            <div class="wrap">

              <div class="fix-12-12 left">
                <h5 class="bold uppercase ae-2 fromLeft margin-bottom-1 opacity-3">Section 5</h5>
                <h1 class=" ae-2 fromLeft left subtitle underline margin-bottom-7 icon_left">
                  <i class="far fa-lightbulb-on"></i> Learning Recap and Takeaways
                </h1>
                <h2 class="small normal margin-bottom-2 ae-2 fromLeft opacity-3">What did we learn in this section?</h2>
                <div class="fix-12-12">
                  <ul class="grid fixedSpaces equal left grid-71">
                    <li class="col-4-12 ae-3">
                      <div class="col-12-12 ae-2 cell-100 rounded padding-3 equalElement verticalCenter">
                        <h4 class="big margin-bottom-2 text-yellow icon_right">
                        <i class="far fa-lightbulb-on"></i> Lesson #1</h4>
                        <p class=" normal">Opportunities for changing your syllabus and experimenting with new ways your syllabus can provide more intentional support for students from minoritized racial/ethnic groups.</p>
                      </div>
                    </li>
                    <li class="col-4-12 ae-4">
                      <div class="col-12-12 ae-2 cell-100 rounded padding-3 equalElement verticalCenter">
